writing an anthology

00:52:44.240 --> 00:52:51.420
for having published a poem
[inaudible] and, you know,

00:52:51.420 --> 00:52:54.270
there's been history
for [inaudible].

00:52:54.270 --> 00:52:58.280
You use phrases that
[inaudible] you use the language

00:52:58.280 --> 00:53:01.580
of his core [inaudible]
like women.

00:53:01.580 --> 00:53:03.880
Isn't that okay?

